panels.description: Numbers of GitHub events in all repositories hourly

targets.rawSql:
select
  time,
  value as "Number of GitHub events hourly"
from
  sevents_h
where
  $__timeFilter(time)
order by
  time

list.name: projects
list.query: select value_s from gha_vars where name = 'projects_partial_html'

current.text:
Hexa Policy Orchestrator Home dashboard

Links:

  • Postgres SQL file, database dumps.
  • TSDB series definition (search for name: GitHub activity).
  • Grafana dashboard JSON.
  • Developer documentation.
  • Direct link.

Description

  • First we're displaying links to all CNCF projects defined.
  • Next we're showing current project's hourly activity - this is the number of all GitHub events that happened for Hexa Policy Orchestrator project hourly.
  • This also includes bots activity (most other dashboards skip bot activity).
  • Next we're showing HTML panel that shows all CNCF projects icons and links.
  • Next there is a dashboard that shows a list of all dashboards defined for Hexa Policy Orchestrator project.
